evidence.claim: Medicaid Complete mentions adherence to HIPAA standards for security and privacy of health information.
The company emphasizes FHIR for data exchange in health records.
Medicaid Complete appears to work with EHRs compliant with healthcare data standards.
References to X12 EDI standards for electronic health information interchange were found in their documentation.

icp.icp_reason: No evidence of using or requiring X12 transactions or EDI solutions for healthcare data exchange.
